2011-07-31  heisvoid  <heisvoid@gmail.com>
  * Release ver. 0.3
  * Remove prdefined variables CHP, COMBATII and PACK
  * Add WIN32 (MinGW MSYS) supports
    - Add headers and libraries for WIN32 build and running
    - Implement WIN32 configuration file selection routine
    - Make forwarding functions for WIN32 findfirst/findnext ()
  * Make platform independent basename ()
  * Change configuration file path in setup script
  * Revise SDL palette setting routine

2011-07-27  heisvoid  <heisvoid@gmail.com>

  * Release ver. 0.2
  * Change music file prefix from 'music' to 'track'
  * Change music encoding quality in setup script
  * Change softmax.fli playback FPS from 14 to 13
  * Add SDL_QUIT event handling routine
  * Add 'center' option which forces window position center
  * Forward video data copy functions in ttl, chp and pack
  * Change instructions valgrind cannot handle
  * Make logging function for wrappers
  * Make script based launcher
  * Forward the following functions
    - dos_findfirst ()
    - dos_findnext ()
    - vsprintf ()
    - printf ()
    - fclose ()
    - memmove ()
    - memset ()
    - memcpy ()
    - strcat ()
    - strlen ()
    - rand ()
    - putch ()
    - strcmp ()
    - puts ()
    - abs ()
    - strrchr ()
    - exit ()
  * Fix: uninitialized variable problem in chp
  * Fix: memory leak in log.c

